Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用右手碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最後的炸藥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把它當作是Nice 小心引爆的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是抵抗的話就殺了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ennis 你在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ennis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人怎麼樣了我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人倒是沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為那傢伙只是個渣滓呢 還挺有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不那麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 雖說我和你們約好活下來的一方由我幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那傢伙還生死未卜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huey是你的戀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不老不死是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定會威脅Huey以奪取不老不死的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人只有他一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是你唯一的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無論如何都要保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我和你結婚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就成為那Huey的兒子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我也是你們的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當不當真隨你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的同伴不一樣 我不會背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會從Huey那兒奪走不死的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無論我是否擁有不死的力量 都絕對死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也默默地相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對死不了的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會經過一條河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不想被警察抓住的話 就從那兒跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的答覆刻在那邊的屋頂上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想扔的話把刀扔過來也無所謂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會躲開的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死者與普通人同樣歌頌人生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jaccuzi平時是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一旦下了決心就絕不會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺那刺青的時候 他也沒哭過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼他平時那麼愛哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 做好心理準備了吧 刺青男
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的時候一定是非努力不可的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以平時就多哭哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把最想哭的時候流的眼淚在現在全流完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓非努力不可的時候流不出眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nick先下去 和回收組的人匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊握拳頭攻擊對方就能射出子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 雖說發生了點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個距離就足以把你燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼想說的嗎 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是「鐵路追蹤者」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後能和兩位說話 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你們能答應我一個任性的請求的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別過來 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 燃燒吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Czes Czes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 Czes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼不吞噬我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 赤手空拳想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 從剛才開始 敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是「鐵路追蹤者」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吃沒有吃完的Czes啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 怎麼能讓它得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jacuzzi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 得快給你止血才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個吧 那新型炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成功了 寶物也到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jaccuzi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前可能是哭得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多哭出來的份就算是把你的份也哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把Nice的份也哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後即使遇到傷心的事 也千萬別哭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jaccuzi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就料到會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前的人造人也一樣 得到了過多的知識後就背叛了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會一下子殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你好好受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 對Ennis幹了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想問問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 Maiza 為什麼我們沒死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們 是你們喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前燒過手套和倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒人頭還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把右手放在他頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ennis 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡想著「我要吞噬」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ennis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 血紅的東西不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Czes呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jacuzzi 剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「鐵路追蹤者」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jacuzzi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 還在猶豫些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要 只要再把右手伸上去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼傷癒合了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很簡單呀 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 「鐵路追蹤者」會一口吃掉一個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完後發現Czes是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吃的東西還回來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 這樣就說得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了謊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說是要去紐約見家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是去見朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是 將來也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Czes果然是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓大家擔心還撒了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最痛苦的是Czes自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Czes是個很好的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 交給我Isaac吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 Czes 交給Isaac就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 笑笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~ Isaac Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Czes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也把我吞噬了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼蠢話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有很多話想和Isaac他們說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我吞噬並了把我的遺言傳達給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想說的話就自己去說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道救你的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 Szilard的知識已經全都給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了那老頭子還是有價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是Firo 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ennis
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你應該已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想親口聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們在笑些什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac 連Miria也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽吧 Dallas‧Genoard的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼還活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 據Firo說 我們和你們一樣成了不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 很可惜 我們和你們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我們希望你們能對自己的所做所為負責
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半永久性地讓你們沉沒於哈得遜河底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想一口氣吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但打你揍你也奈何不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K哥真善心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們在河裡老死一定會很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就算是餞別了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 太過分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你哥哥殘忍地殺害了我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前 就在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我們不會道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 我們打心裡向你表示哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能做到的只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈得遜河嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你們扔了 那就隨我們撿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 所有權還在親人手裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算把哥哥怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某個研究所全面調查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把哥哥撈上來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他能從淹沒的痛苦中解脫出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我們見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人可是你們家的仇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來像是借口也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但殺死Lamord和Jeffery並不是我的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這男人擅自的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是老大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來救我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣該接受教訓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他能從河底的地獄中獲救的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想哥哥也是會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了 Gandor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eve小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~ Ennis Firo還有Maiza
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了啊 好朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們那麼精神 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 Ennis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子叫Czes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊 Ennis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他當Ennis的弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精心準備的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Czes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maiza
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了吞噬這個男人才來這城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆認識嗎 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是的啊 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Czes說過是來看朋友的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 就那樣把右手放在我頭上把我吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在那之前吞噬他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 把右手伸向Maiza
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼呀 這是掩飾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假裝關心 之後再慢慢吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦 Czes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦 就像從前那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maiza
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本應再也回不到那船上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見你啊 Maiza
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Firo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maiza先生 我全都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Firo 沒必要那麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Maiza先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把永遠活著的痛苦給了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼呀 Maiza先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們根本不介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想高呼「不死真是太好了 喲吼」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太明白 但「喲吼」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲吼 打起精神來 Maiza
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對頭領和矢車先生就騙他們說沉默就能長壽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀 Firo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為慶祝新幹部的誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來來 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被請來參加這麼豐盛的宴會了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個見面禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grad 這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他察覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最終還是沒能阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下意識中我就這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在曼哈頓等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠等下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你 請你來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是曼哈頓 但範圍也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還沒把我的名字告訴她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 雖說還要等我還清了Gandor兄弟的人情之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能拯救很多小孩了啊 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是毒電波啊 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據英國聖誕老人說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於手機電波 家庭交流變少
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩沉迷於電腦 爸爸在搞外遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽出去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭破裂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以我們要阻止它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是對策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們沒有變老
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~ 真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:23:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不知道為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們經常再生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得慶祝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家叫上 每天都開Party呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac 生日快樂
